Subject: Frequent Paper Jams with Canon PIXMA MG3620

Dear Customer Support, I am reaching out to address an issue I've been facing with my Canon PIXMA MG3620 printer purchased from your store. Recently, I have encountered frequent paper jams while performing duplex printing You can reach me at carlosm@gmail.com.. This problem disrupts my workflow, and I suspect it might be a defect with the printer model. Could you please provide guidance on the steps I should take to resolve this issue? Is there any troubleshooting I can try? Additionally, could you let me know if there are options for a replacement or repair under warranty? Thank you for your assistance My name is Carlos Mendoza.. Best regards, <name>.
